@startuml
title Video Suggestion System State Diagram

state Start as [*]
state RequestReceived
state UserIdentified
state VideosGathering
state VideosEnriched
state VideosSent as [Done]

Start --> RequestReceived : Request received
RequestReceived --> UserIdentified : Identify user
UserIdentified --> VideosGathering : Gather videos
VideosGathering --> VideosEnriched : Videos gathered
VideosEnriched --> VideosSent : Enrich videos
VideosSent --> : End

note right
  This diagram models the normal flow of the video suggestion system.
  Each state represents a step in processing the request.
  Transitions are triggered by system events or conditions.
end note

@enduml
